<p>I have two WPF Textbox, Textbox1 and Textbox2. The Texbox2 changes with user types in anything in Textbox1 and also Textbox2.Text need to be loaded/saved to data source. I can either bind the bind the Textbox2.Text to the Textbox1.Text like</p>  <pre><code>&lt;TextBox Name="Textbox2" Text="{Binding Text, ElementName=Textbox1}"/&gt;  </code></pre>  <p>or to data source </p>  <pre><code>&lt;TextBox Name="Textbox2" Text="{Binding Path="AProperty"}"/&gt; </code></pre>  <p>How can I have both?</p>